posThenNotZero:{a:ZZ}->(IsPositive a)->(NotZero a)
posThenNotZero {a = (Pos (S k))} Positive = PositiveZ

|||Rewrites a=b as a=1*b
rewriteRightAsOneTimesRight: {a:ZZ}->{b:ZZ}->(a=b)->(a=(1*b))
