productOneThenNumbersOne (Pos (S (S _))) (Pos (S (S _))) Refl impossible
productOneThenNumbersOne (Pos (S (S _))) (NegS _) Refl impossible
productOneThenNumbersOne (NegS Z) (Pos Z) Refl impossible
